               <msContents>
                  <summary>Chants called Ziq, መጽሐፈ፡ ዚቅ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="109v" facs="003">Fols 1r–109v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1979Mashaf">Maṣḥafa ziq</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ናሁ፡ ወጠንኩ፡ ጽሒፈ፡ ዚቅ፡ ዘአስተጋ[ብ]ዕዎ፡ ሊቃውንተ፡ ጐንደር፡ እምፀዋትወ፡ ዜማሁ፡ ለአቡነ፡ ያሬድ፡ ቢጸ፡ ሱራፌል፡ ጸሎቱ፡ ወበረከቱ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
